{"type":"meta","topicId":"F19-TP4","title":"Available Page Size Selector"}
{"type":"given","text":"The Available list displays more results than a single page and the pagination shell is visible."}
{"type":"when","text":"The admin changes the per-page selector value."}
{"type":"then","text":"The controller requests the new page size, reloads page 1 for that size, saves the preference for future sessions, and keeps summary/Prev-Next states accurate."}
